[
  {
    "text": "Jimmy Carl, welcome to the show.",
    "uid": "8e82e3a19fed8993",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you very much. I'm a big fan of it.",
    "uid": "83bf941ecfd7e2c5",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 1.6,
    "end": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm kind of nervous about talking to you in a weird way,",
    "uid": "0cab47e918c5e0aa",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 4.0,
    "end": 6.8
  },
  {
    "text": "because I like the show.",
    "uid": "6c3796ebbd32c379",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 6.8,
    "end": 8.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I really like you as a kind of cultural entity.",
    "uid": "ec0df97f737f0415",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 8.96,
    "end": 14.08
  },
  {
    "text": "I think it's a really interesting kind of journey you've had.",
    "uid": "6e0c8bb0c386dc1e",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 14.08,
    "end": 16.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And I get so much from this show.",
    "uid": "42d37af24483b299",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 16.48,
    "end": 18.56
  },
  {
    "text": "You know that phrase, I think you use it probably more than any other phrase.",
    "uid": "27dcae8dd41695c2",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 18.56,
    "end": 22.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Does it grow corn?",
    "uid": "58996a612d3bdd9b",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 22.64,
    "end": 24.0
  },
  {
    "text": "And for me, this show really kind of grows corn.",
    "uid": "ba60f0d4eee5ad35",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 24.0,
    "end": 26.56
  },
  {
    "text": "There's so many little things that I've taken from this",
    "uid": "0484d2177f777c56",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 26.56,
    "end": 29.28
  },
  {
    "text": "that I've kind of gone, oh, I'm going to do that.",
    "uid": "d8243e193dc90090",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 29.28,
    "end": 31.84
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to do something with that.",
    "uid": "05bf4caf9309e045",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 31.84,
    "end": 33.36
  },
  {
    "text": "So kind of the practical application of the wisdom,",
    "uid": "451ce54583fb6078",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 33.36,
    "end": 36.8
  },
  {
    "text": "what you get out of people seems to be very easy to integrate into life.",
    "uid": "6aa3408c369ced80",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 36.8,
    "end": 41.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Right, so the bar's being set high for you today, then if you start.",
    "uid": "444b6341001a2c97",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 41.84,
    "end": 45.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, I better.",
    "uid": "3b7c631aa1ad11ab",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 45.28,
    "end": 46.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, I mean, sticking around is sort of what I do.",
    "uid": "e83cbff758088d8a",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 46.24,
    "end": 48.64
  },
  {
    "text": "So the other thing is like, I kind of get more nervous being myself than being",
    "uid": "9c97b42268cfc6b7",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 48.64,
    "end": 52.8
  },
  {
    "text": "sort of the comedic persona, the you know, just being funny.",
    "uid": "ab17f705e45a3d81",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 52.8,
    "end": 57.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Just being your things being funny, I find very easy.",
    "uid": "e89297aa9c7e04ee",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 57.44,
    "end": 60.32
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a, it's a interesting sort of life lesson.",
    "uid": "b91722f806904fa3",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 60.32,
    "end": 62.88
  },
  {
    "text": "The idea of like, what do you find easy that other people find difficult?",
    "uid": "56b9f65be3913934",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 62.88,
    "end": 66.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Go for that. Do that for a living.",
    "uid": "97779c33355caac5",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 66.0,
    "end": 68.16
  },
  {
    "text": "That's, that's, there's going to be money there.",
    "uid": "ec116f10efdd5d70",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 68.16,
    "end": 70.16
  },
  {
    "text": "There's going to be, there's going to be some gold.",
    "uid": "76a10e37f0bceffe",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 70.16,
    "end": 71.92
  },
  {
    "text": "You're going to be okay.",
    "uid": "873bfac2410d8621",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 71.92,
    "end": 72.96
  },
  {
    "text": "If you find easy and everyone else is going, that's impossible.",
    "uid": "343ffb3e8f16dc73",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 72.96,
    "end": 75.68
  },
  {
    "text": "So you're standing up in front of people being funny.",
    "uid": "b9594727b27c9aa9",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 75.68,
    "end": 77.6
  },
  {
    "text": "I found very easy.",
    "uid": "cd58ce8e29e685e5",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 77.6,
    "end": 78.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Like these kind of conversations, I slightly, you slightly second guess yourself.",
    "uid": "6b746b7c6c51d054",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 78.64,
    "end": 82.8
  },
  {
    "text": "It's what you're used to.",
    "uid": "dc637615618e4232",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 82.8,
    "end": 84.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I think it's what you spend a lot of time becoming a climateist.",
    "uid": "b400d8a66815b8c8",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 84.0,
    "end": 87.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, I suppose.",
    "uid": "3a7caf3efab9ec5b",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 88.16,
    "end": 89.04
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, it's just that thing of, I've always said in comedy,",
    "uid": "d1dd3982388ea830",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 89.04,
    "end": 91.76
  },
  {
    "text": "people sort of talk about how many years they've been doing comedy and it seems",
    "uid": "dc98548cfe154cc7",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 91.76,
    "end": 94.32
  },
  {
    "text": "It's kind of, it's like when you're in an airline pilot,",
    "uid": "e490905832e465a7",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 95.52,
    "end": 97.84
  },
  {
    "text": "they've got a really good view on it.",
    "uid": "c153964725307acd",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 97.84,
    "end": 98.88
  },
  {
    "text": "They talk about how many hours they've got in the sky.",
    "uid": "9c03afb50e458581",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 98.88,
    "end": 101.2
  },
  {
    "text": "And for me, like, there's no substitute for stage time.",
    "uid": "ee908c0c20ef3ad8",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 101.2,
    "end": 105.52
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'm sure for you, there's no substitute for this, but actually doing it.",
    "uid": "58b77b97707860a9",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 105.52,
    "end": 109.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Everything else is, it's kind of, it doesn't matter how many years you've had a podcast.",
    "uid": "629fd782392ba1b3",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 109.04,
    "end": 113.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I think something about the frequency of your show as well.",
    "uid": "1e19ec77322046f2",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 113.2,
    "end": 115.84
  },
  {
    "text": "It's the, it's kind of it's always there, there's always something new.",
    "uid": "63f6a9cd02980ed9",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 115.84,
    "end": 118.48
  },
  {
    "text": "You talk about the most important question to ask yourself being what you want.",
    "uid": "38af511f8e51e364",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 120.0,
    "end": 124.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, I mean, I took about that in all of a lot of study,",
    "uid": "aefe4dc7dca106e9",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 125.68,
    "end": 127.84
  },
  {
    "text": "studied and was very interested in sort of NLP.",
    "uid": "b93d6ff9542fc12e",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 128.88,
    "end": 130.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And that question of what do you want in the micro in the macro?",
    "uid": "73ffa1e7079f4f5c",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 130.96,
    "end": 134.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Being, being the absolute key in sort of life.",
    "uid": "b3d88902b50ece59",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 134.64,
    "end": 138.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Because people sort of, I suppose it's, it's that thing of going,",
    "uid": "670fe9c760a8417d",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 139.44,
    "end": 143.6
  },
  {
    "text": "what does something represent? People, someone might say, well, I want a Ferrari.",
    "uid": "0674db098055bb0c",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 143.6,
    "end": 146.8
  },
  {
    "text": "But why? If you sort of dig a little deep, you can't just ask once,",
    "uid": "bfd94359e4e4bb70",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 148.64,
    "end": 151.76
  },
  {
    "text": "what do you want what I want a Ferrari and a Rolex and all of the trappings.",
    "uid": "5d57a4ccb57eefb7",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 151.76,
    "end": 155.76
  },
  {
    "text": "But actually what they want is status.",
    "uid": "7706f98b871866fc",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 155.76,
    "end": 157.84
  },
  {
    "text": "So it's kind of asking yourself, what game are you going to play?",
    "uid": "28bc3a6c6fbc583a",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 158.72,
    "end": 161.44
  },
  {
    "text": "I read a lot of that, Renée Girard stuff about sort of magnetic desires.",
    "uid": "5308a20419e5100c",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 161.44,
    "end": 167.44
  },
  {
    "text": "So this idea that you've got what you really want.",
    "uid": "2dd503025bdaa117",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 167.44,
    "end": 170.56
  },
  {
    "text": "I kind of a fundamental level, it's about you.",
    "uid": "0b7c043d2a4dc874",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 170.64,
    "end": 174.16
  },
  {
    "text": "And what you perceive, you should have compared to others.",
    "uid": "24f8a95bd4c5f821",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 174.72,
    "end": 177.76
  },
  {
    "text": "So this idea of kind of being honest about what you want and why you want it.",
    "uid": "35131ef70c63dab2",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 178.32,
    "end": 181.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, splitting apart what is a genuine desire that's come from you, that's been self-authored.",
    "uid": "ea0e267de28c273c",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 182.08,
    "end": 188.32
  },
  {
    "text": "And what is just the things that you've taken from the way you dealt with past trauma and what your",
    "uid": "a19889c8a3da9a71",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 189.04,
    "end": 195.2
  },
  {
    "text": "parents valued and what society says that you should and the paths of least resistance and",
    "uid": "b1aa4e2f2574c857",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 195.2,
    "end": 200.4
  },
  {
    "text": "your genetic predisposition, this beautiful quote that says, ultimately happiness comes down to",
    "uid": "2e5819f87baaf978",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 200.4,
    "end": 207.04
  },
  {
    "text": "choosing between the discomfort of becoming aware of our mental afflictions and the discomfort of",
    "uid": "63ee09b7eebcd705",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 207.04,
    "end": 212.24
  },
  {
    "text": "becoming ruled by them. And it's a lot. I mean, it's like, I don't think anyone gets there.",
    "uid": "8400c689b2d7b45c",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 212.24,
    "end": 218.32
  },
  {
    "text": "By the way, I think there's there's, there's slightly, I think sometimes I want to hear people",
    "uid": "3e5b11a3a3dc5108",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 218.88,
    "end": 222.16
  },
  {
    "text": "kind of into talking about this stuff. There's a sense of, oh, you know, I'm in light and now and",
    "uid": "0fedb0847b3c7be3",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 222.16,
    "end": 227.6
  },
  {
    "text": "I know knowing that you know, you only want that thing because you've got that thing and I want the",
    "uid": "06d4a1f3207f4766",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 227.6,
    "end": 233.52
  },
  {
    "text": "new iPhone because you've got the new iPhone. Knowing that doesn't really make any difference because when you're",
    "uid": "ca890d9faca1f847",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 233.52,
    "end": 239.52
  },
  {
    "text": "out there in the world, you've still got to live a life and do something correct. But it's about what that will",
    "uid": "eb7cc2a61b967e6d",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 239.52,
    "end": 244.4
  },
  {
    "text": "storebook. I thought was phenomenal. The status gate. I mean, all these books are great. Actually,",
    "uid": "80b14de7ca3831b3",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 244.4,
    "end": 250.24
  },
  {
    "text": "it's a really interesting sort of, underrated, right? It's wonderful. But that thing of like going,",
    "uid": "95aa158c17c56548",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 250.32,
    "end": 255.6
  },
  {
    "text": "why don't you pick what status game you play in? You can have anything. You can't have everything.",
    "uid": "a0a418b86811bf7a",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 255.6,
    "end": 261.92
  },
  {
    "text": "It's that thing of just that the words seem to be very important to me. The idea of saying,",
    "uid": "5c4d34ecd5035f2a",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 261.92,
    "end": 266.08
  },
  {
    "text": "you can work for anything in life to a kid, as well as you can have anything. Is the difference between",
    "uid": "50a4fadf76a91b77",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 267.36,
    "end": 273.6
  },
  {
    "text": "ambition and entitlement? Some doubt. Some lovely thing you sent out the other day.",
    "uid": "9c84a1c3fee14192",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 273.84,
    "end": 280.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes. That difference between ambition and entitlement being ambition. Ambition is when you expect",
    "uid": "bd024b26ad427c69",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 280.64,
    "end": 289.04
  },
  {
    "text": "yourself to close the gap between what you have and what you want. And entitlement is when you expect others",
    "uid": "3b011b767a73caf1",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 289.04,
    "end": 294.4
  },
  {
    "text": "to close the gap between what you have and what you want. Yeah, that thing of like agency seems",
    "uid": "3b6b1405876f5c31",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 294.4,
    "end": 299.84
  },
  {
    "text": "that's very high on my list of getting back to what you want. Agency, I want the, I want control",
    "uid": "98c5409bfe035ff7",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 300.8,
    "end": 307.68
  },
  {
    "text": "to be in here. I think it's better to be a stand-up. I mean, the thing I've been thinking about recently",
    "uid": "4b2a2439e64b229a",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 307.68,
    "end": 312.88
  },
  {
    "text": "is being stoic, doing less better. Being a stand-up is a great job. And there's so many stand-ups that get",
    "uid": "e495b9735ae29251",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 312.88,
    "end": 319.76
  },
  {
    "text": "the job of being a stand-up. And then they want to be an actor. And I go, you're mad. It's not as good a job.",
    "uid": "dbeb84c1bcea9baa",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 319.76,
    "end": 327.04
  },
  {
    "text": "It's better to do a podcast than to have a TV show. Because you're in charge. You're in boss.",
    "uid": "ccd05b720d7f430a",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 327.12,
    "end": 333.12
  },
  {
    "text": "You're kind of, you're in a cancel proof, not particularly bothered about that. But the idea of going,",
    "uid": "c9b59199fd82c7c9",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 333.12,
    "end": 337.84
  },
  {
    "text": "you're in charge and you've got agency and you can do what you want. Well, there's a level of, there's a huge",
    "uid": "eba9dc09a8144140",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 337.84,
    "end": 341.28
  },
  {
    "text": "power to that. There's a level of narcissism, I think, that comes with believing that you would be able",
    "uid": "fa70d294ed7b8d7f",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 341.28,
    "end": 349.52
  },
  {
    "text": "to beat somebody else at them doing one thing while you're doing two things. Okay, so you think that",
    "uid": "74dbbbf48099907a",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 349.52,
    "end": 355.52
  },
  {
    "text": "you're going to be a better podcast than the guy that just as a podcast while it's",
    "uid": "7373c389253f76a7",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 355.52,
    "end": 359.12
  },
  {
    "text": "trying to do a podcast and run a business and be on TV and fly around the world and do all of these things.",
    "uid": "cd90e10044efc313",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 359.12,
    "end": 364.72
  },
  {
    "text": "It's also that thing of like going, if your aim is sort of happiness, I think having a process driven",
    "uid": "62c29c3ae513cb99",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 364.72,
    "end": 370.8
  },
  {
    "text": "ambition rather than an outcome driven ambition. Like what do you want to do rather than what you want to be?",
    "uid": "9937675b2fb1dea0",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 370.8,
    "end": 376.88
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, so that idea of going that you do a podcast and you live for it. It seems to be pretty",
    "uid": "2cc02ac0c77e5ce2",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 377.76,
    "end": 383.12
  },
  {
    "text": "much or you care about and you're loving it and you're, you kind of embody that and it gets back to that",
    "uid": "db1f64fee83b5fb7",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 383.12,
    "end": 388.4
  },
  {
    "text": "novel thing of like what's play for you? What's easy for you? What's play? What's just what's fun? No one's",
    "uid": "0df3cd9b289dbb3a",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 388.4,
    "end": 394.24
  },
  {
    "text": "going to put this effort in. Look around, look at the 4K cameras, whatever. No one's putting this effort",
    "uid": "a01076f8e8244af6",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 394.24,
    "end": 399.12
  },
  {
    "text": "in that doesn't really care about it. So someone trying to fake it and go, well, I won't want",
    "uid": "8db1a669ea77558b",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 399.12,
    "end": 403.12
  },
  {
    "text": "what he's getting for that. I want the end, revenue. It's like, well, no, that's the, you're playing",
    "uid": "a07488c531faf8d7",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 403.12,
    "end": 408.24
  },
  {
    "text": "in the wrong game. There's a really great quote from Mark Manson where he talks about the most",
    "uid": "82941b35c99ac8aa",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 408.32,
    "end": 412.32
  },
  {
    "text": "important question to ask yourself is what pain are you willing to endure in your life, rather than what",
    "uid": "9190aa19276daa53",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 412.32,
    "end": 416.88
  },
  {
    "text": "pleasure do you want? Because any pleasure or any pursuit that you want is going to come with an in-kind",
    "uid": "7514a81a39722309",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 416.88,
    "end": 421.84
  },
  {
    "text": "payment of pain. Well, even your stuff did the fatigue, the road, everything else. But that thing of like,",
    "uid": "01abbb6def58be0a",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 421.84,
    "end": 427.6
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, the all self help is hard choices now, easy life later. Everything is the marshmallow test.",
    "uid": "a081a1e296847232",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 427.6,
    "end": 434.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Everything is about saying, look, you know, the famous marshmallow test of Gifekid, you know,",
    "uid": "f6a79a841a8cf131",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 434.88,
    "end": 439.2
  },
  {
    "text": "one marshmallow now or two later. That seems to be a really good indicator in life of going,",
    "uid": "e59234455e7f9b11",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 439.2,
    "end": 444.24
  },
  {
    "text": "what are you willing to and and and work really is work is the sacrifice for later. And it's really",
    "uid": "cb8b287f51f5f2f3",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 444.24,
    "end": 451.28
  },
  {
    "text": "about that timeframe. There are probably the biggest thing I got from this show and from following you",
    "uid": "3e61d6cee63a8a20",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 451.28,
    "end": 457.28
  },
  {
    "text": "was that idea of serving yourself in 24 hours. You have to serve someone, what are you going to do",
    "uid": "ff20cfde93853871",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 457.28,
    "end": 463.12
  },
  {
    "text": "today that you tomorrow will appreciate? Yeah. Because if there's something about a day,",
    "uid": "fa7ed5037e630b34",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 464.08,
    "end": 469.6
  },
  {
    "text": "seems about the right timeframe. Like if it's if it's in six months time and you're trying to go to",
    "uid": "61d1b517866ac541",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 469.6,
    "end": 474.24
  },
  {
    "text": "the gym and motivate yourself by I'm going to look great in six months it's like, ah, I don't know.",
    "uid": "0c635f0366f4493f",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 474.24,
    "end": 479.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know if you can do that. I don't think that's a motivator because written on my fridge,",
    "uid": "f1fcf9543d315185",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 479.04,
    "end": 483.36
  },
  {
    "text": "what would you tomorrow want you today to do? It's a great, I think there's a book in that. I think",
    "uid": "e533f6d4f4529970",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 483.36,
    "end": 488.8
  },
  {
    "text": "genuinely I think it's such a powerful, you've got me writing, you have told me to write five different",
    "uid": "924fcd64bc8650be",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 488.8,
    "end": 494.4
  },
  {
    "text": "books over the last week that we'd spend together. But I like the idea of that thing of going because it's",
    "uid": "fa7f0a738dbc40d5",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 494.4,
    "end": 499.2
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, you listen to a podcast but the book seems to be the book in the course seems to be the thing that",
    "uid": "452bfdfe2c04460d",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 499.84,
    "end": 504.08
  },
  {
    "text": "it's just a way of getting all of your thoughts on this together. It's a great treatment. Yeah.",
    "uid": "e070125f21168868",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 504.08,
    "end": 508.8
  },
  {
    "text": "I think that idea of like your the you know what are you going to do that's going to make you",
    "uid": "fb2ccf46c18d6a7d",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 509.92,
    "end": 514.48
  },
  {
    "text": "happy in 24 hours and that's really about saying what your ambitions should be",
    "uid": "ba77cfb19a701947",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 514.48,
    "end": 520.0
  },
  {
    "text": "feelings not things. What's the difference? Well, the idea that you go, what how do I want to feel",
    "uid": "2950a9778b0f44fd",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 521.28,
    "end": 527.04
  },
  {
    "text": "is something that you go well that's that's an ambition you don't have I want to feel happy I want to",
    "uid": "2c68430e09239cc4",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 527.6,
    "end": 531.28
  },
  {
    "text": "focus on content and I want to feel healthy I want to feel fulfilled wanting those things wanting material",
    "uid": "c394538a6953d2d4",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 531.28,
    "end": 536.72
  },
  {
    "text": "things the reason you want the material thing is to give you the feeling. So just cut out the middle man.",
    "uid": "53c5f78e8e96b244",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 536.72,
    "end": 541.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, I mean it's easy for me to say I'm sure",
    "uid": "e80e36fa65c1cbd4",
    "source": "Chris_Williamson - All_Self-Help_Boils_Down_To_One_Truth_-_Jimmy_Carr_4K",
    "start": 541.36,
    "end": 544.72
  }
]